window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Magnus has been focused on his present, the loops and time shifts behind him, but that is not all in the past. There is also a throne that must be held, a historic event that must be protected, and a kingdom that needs him to rule.</p> <p>From the shores of modern day Amelia Island to Scotland's medieval age, from his family in 17th century Balloch castle to his mother holding his kingdom in Riaghalbane for his son, Magnus must once again draw his sword to battle for those he loves and has promised to protect.</p> <p>Perfect for fans of Outlander, Thor, and Bridget Jones’s Diary, this Highlander romance weaves time travel, steamy passion, humor, and beach romance charm in a blend of contemporary and historical twists, with Science Fiction surprises. Book 19 in a 21-book saga sweeps listeners from modern Florida to Scottish history and beyond. Dive into this time travel romance today!</p>"; 
